The nature preserve , occupying about 220,000 hectares , has 102 giant pandas living wild .
Zhang said that the preserve will dispatch frequent patrols and rescue giant pandas in danger of starvation .
ATTENTION - ADDS information on sub-species of giant panda ///
China has 163 giant pandas in captivity .
What is worse , arrow bamboo on another 1,950 hectares which blossomed in 1993 has not grown tall enough for consumption .
The bamboo blooming in the early 1980s caused the deaths of about 250 giant pandas .
